    },
    {
      "id": "n6sYr7lZAs13-eIq1X1Mr",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1961.724467800352,
      "y": 235.78498366607096,
      "width": 514.1196899414062,
      "height": 350,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "al",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1339014494,
      "version": 339,
      "versionNonce": 1110594014,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1778276689063,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "6M drivers\n3M active\n3M / 5 = 600K TPS\n\nConsistency of matching\n1. AT most one request per ride\n2. At most one driver sent to fulfill request per ride\n\nwhile (noMatch) {\n    driver = nextDriver\n    lock(driver)\n    sendNotification(driver)\n    wait(10s)\n}",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "6M drivers\n3M active\n3M / 5 = 600K TPS\n\nConsistency of matching\n1. AT most one request per ride\n2. At most one driver sent to fulfill request per ride\n\nwhile (noMatch) {\n    driver = nextDriver\n    lock(driver)\n    sendNotification(driver)\n    wait(10s)\n}",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
